divs: Sighting DetailsThis was a hot night for activity in the Air over NYC.. Here we see a golden white orb flying gently across the Mid-Town sky heading West towards Jersey.. The Object is between my house and about 79th street. Its near enough to see if its a Helicopter or Plane and you can clearly see its neither... This is from 111709 v456
